citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 145-219 on
06/04/2015. Access to the property was blocked by a closed privacy gate. A message was left on the phone
number provided to the ACI.
